title: 820-00840 No boot
message:
Nothing on screen or HDMI through usb-c, trackpad is clickable
Cpu gets hot but coils L7410/20/30 are all at 0v all other coils are measuring what they should be

Board has minor signs of liquid arround Q8400 area but no corrosion anywhere to be seen

title: 820-00840 No boot
message: Sounds like bad CPU to me very common if any liquid near CPU.

title: 820-00840 No boot
message:
Liquid spill is a great danger for the new boards; CPU is very fragile.
Did you check USB activity?

title: 820-00840 No boot
message: Cant see any liquid evidence on the top of the board, how can I check for usb activity?

title: 820-00840 No boot
message:
An USB mouse get light?
Better to check with an USB OSX pendrive, with Link LED; if flashes, that confirm 100% USB activity.
Disconnect internall SSD for this test.

title: 820-00840 No boot
message:
No blinking on thumbdrive, GTVR_FCCM is reading 0v is this normal?
Usb-c amp meter just came in and its reading 19.7v 0.55a when on is this normal?

title: 820-00840 No boot
message:
Seems to be low.
But your board doesn't really work, so cannot expect normal value.
